general notes

mongosh commands (terminal) :

show dbs = show all database
switch [name] = switch to different database (file) eg. switch admin
db.createCollection("[name]") = create new collection
db.dropDatabase() = delete database you are in

database requirements: 
- create task:
  - task name
  - description:
  - status:
  - due date: 
- edit task: (edit database)
- delete task: (try to implement restore option)

calendar:
- database of different backgrounds
- create schedule:
  - task
  - colour
  - schedule name
  - time range
  - description

notification:
- overdue tasks
- added task
- deleted task
